# Build artifacts inside corpus project checkouts.
#
# The checkouts under `bench/projects/<id>/checkout/` are either pinned
# git submodules (P02) or vendored source trees (P01, P03). In all
# cases we keep the *source* committed (or pointer-committed) and let
# Maven generate `target/` etc. at bench-run time. None of that should
# pollute the parent repo's working tree or sneak into a commit.

# Maven build output, anywhere in any checkout.
**/checkout/target/
**/checkout/**/target/

# IDE scaffolding.
**/checkout/.idea/
**/checkout/.vscode/
**/checkout/*.iml
**/checkout/**/*.iml

# Local OS detritus.
**/checkout/.DS_Store
**/checkout/**/.DS_Store

# Per-project benchmark scratch (e.g. captured profiles, run logs).
**/.bench-run/
